metadata.title: Cessna 206
aws::graph::propositions: Mexico operates Cessna 206 aircraft in the Mexican Air Force.
Pakistan Army Aviation operates 4 T-206H aircraft.
Panamanian Air Force operated at least one Cessna 206 from 1984.
Panamanian Air Force operated at least one Cessna 207 from 1984.
Paraguayan Air Force operates 5 U206G aircraft.
Paraguayan Naval Aviation operates 4 U206A/C aircraft.
Paraguayan Army Aviation operates 2 U206G aircraft.
Portuguese Air Force operated 1 Cessna 206 from 1968 to 1974.
Suriname Air Force operates Cessna 206 aircraft.
US Army uses two Cessna 206 aircraft at US Military Academy since 2021.
Uruguayan Air Force operates Cessna 206 aircraft.
